{"hash":"ec5b2a023d11b4d5c45fd895008e7baeaf5a56e1","data":{"post":{"id":"a7b5c8337cbedc9d95d74096cbcb5a6e","category":"알고리즘","sub_category":"Solution","title":"[HackerRank] Absolute Permutation","series_name":"","series_num":0,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F9d41c1ed-b707-4925-a36b-726cc66c7341%2Fhacker-rank-logo.png?table=block&#x26;id=62d1f9a2-d7ad-4c7e-bb71-ee02ff10d667&#x26;width=3260&#x26;userId=&#x26;cache=v2\"></p>\n<br>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/absolute-permutation/problem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Absolute Permutation</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-solve\"><a href=\"#how-to-solve\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>How To Solve</h2>\n<p>단순 순열문제로 판단하고 접근했다가 테스트케이스에서 낭패를 보았다.</p>\n<p>단순히 차이값을 판단하고 <code class=\"language-text\">index</code>를 구하려했는데 그런 문제도 아니였다.</p>\n<p>개인적으로 상당히 까다로웠던 문제였다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>우선 특정 예외조건들은 따로 처리한다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">k === 0</code>이거나 조건이 성립할 수 없을 경우</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>첫 연산은 무조건 <code class=\"language-text\">+</code>연산만 가능하다.</p>\n<p>이후 발생하는 연산은 조건에 맞게 이루어진다. </p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"solution\"><a href=\"#solution\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Solution</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">absolutePermutation</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> k</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> ret <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>k <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      ret<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> ret\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>n <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> k<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> add <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> ret<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> k<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> ret<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> k<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> k <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> add <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span>add\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> ret\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"test-case\"><a href=\"#test-case\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Test-case</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1\n100 2\n\n3 4 1 2 7 8 5 6 11 12 9 10 15 16 13 14 19 20 17 \n18 23 24 21 22 27 28 25 26 31 32 29 30 35 36 33 \n34 39 40 37 38 43 44 41 42 47 48 45 46 51 52 49 \n50 55 56 53 54 59 60 57 58 63 64 61 62 67 68 65 \n66 71 72 69 70 75 76 73 74 79 80 77 78 83 84 81 \n82 87 88 85 86 91 92 89 90 95 96 93 94 99 100 97 98</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"reference\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Reference</h2>\n<span class=\"reference\">\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/akasai/Algorithm-Solutions/blob/master/HackerRank/Implementation/36.Absolute_Permutation.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github</a></p>\n</span>\n","tags":[{"title":"Algorithm","path":"/tag/Algorithm/"},{"title":"HackerRank","path":"/tag/HackerRank/"},{"title":"Javascript","path":"/tag/Javascript/"}],"date":"9월 28 월, 2020","update_date":"9월 28 월, 2020","timeToRead":1,"headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"How To Solve","anchor":"#how-to-solve"},{"depth":2,"value":"Solution","anchor":"#solution"},{"depth":3,"value":"Test-case","anchor":"#test-case"},{"depth":2,"value":"Reference","anchor":"#reference"}]},"related":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Majority Element","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-majority-element/","date":"2020.10.20"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Sliding Window Maximum","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-sliding-window-maximum/","date":"2020.10.19"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Count And Say","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-count-and-say/","date":"2020.10.14"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Add Two Numbers","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-add-two-numbers/","date":"2020.10.13"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Merge Two Binary Tree","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-merge-b-tree/","date":"2020.10.12"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] String Compression","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-string-compression/","date":"2020.10.08"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] First Bad Version","category":"알고리즘","descrip